text: Maintal is the second largest town in Main-Kinzig in Hesse, Germany. It is on the river Main, between Frankfurt am Main and Hanau. == Twin towns == Maintal is twinned with: * Luisant, France (1973) * Moosburg, Austria (1976) * Esztergom, Hungary (1993) * Katerini, Greece (1995) == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Towns in Hesse Category:Main-Kinzig- Kreis
title: Maintal
